    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still firm and the 'new car' scent intact. Every feature and electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that has been stored in a climate-controlled garage.",
