    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly pristine specimen. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our highest standards of excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
